  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quirkbound is an <strong>absurd</strong> and <strong>lighthearted turn-based JRPG</strong> with colorful 2D pixel art, bizarre yet charming enemies, a bangin’ soundtrack, and award-winning* writing that’s sure to warm your heart in a medically non-threatening way. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>*No awards have actually been awarded. Yet.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2711300/extras/12dd269b0160491cc38bc87e8a388cf0.poster.avif?t=1731245171\" width=600 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2711300/extras/12dd269b0160491cc38bc87e8a388cf0.webm?t=1731245171\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2711300/extras/12dd269b0160491cc38bc87e8a388cf0.mp4?t=1731245171\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow the three young heroes Isaac, Clara and Naoto as they journey across the land to recover the Staff of Ultimate Power from the heinous <strong>Varakh</strong> and prevent <strong>the end of the world</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore</strong> and <strong>fight</strong> your way through the otherworldly and box-filled <strong>Basement Dimension</strong> and the luscious and overgrown <strong>Garden Forest</strong>!<strong> </strong>Meet and<strong> talk</strong> to whimsical characters and discover hidden stories!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2711300/extras/7aa73717f7a1b17962143a9a4678909f.poster.avif?t=1731245171\" width=600 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2711300/extras/7aa73717f7a1b17962143a9a4678909f.webm?t=1731245171\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2711300/extras/7aa73717f7a1b17962143a9a4678909f.mp4?t=1731245171\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in strategic turn-based battles against a cast of charming and deadly enemies! <strong>Block, dodge,</strong> and <strong>parry</strong> enemy attacks in real time with our even more award-winning** battle minigame!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2711300/extras/b83d6f9424b7b9c4ebe82dbeaea61d6a.poster.avif?t=1731245171\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2711300/extras/b83d6f9424b7b9c4ebe82dbeaea61d6a.webm?t=1731245171\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2711300/extras/b83d6f9424b7b9c4ebe82dbeaea61d6a.mp4?t=1731245171\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Slash, cast, shield, inspect,</strong> and <strong>stick</strong> your way to victory!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>**Still no awards. Yet.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2711300/extras/7bde79eac639198e8f7503553203df7f.poster.avif?t=1731245171\" width=600 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2711300/extras/7bde79eac639198e8f7503553203df7f.webm?t=1731245171\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2711300/extras/7bde79eac639198e8f7503553203df7f.mp4?t=1731245171\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect powerful <strong>stickers, equipment,</strong> and <strong>spells</strong> to upgrade the party and temporarily satiate your <i>unending hunger for content</i>!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quirkbound is an <strong>absurd</strong> and <strong>lighthearted turn-based JRPG</strong> with colorful 2D pixel art, bizarre yet charming enemies, a bangin’ soundtrack, and award-winning* writing that’s sure to warm your heart in a medically non-threatening way. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>*No awards have actually been awarded. Yet.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2711300/extras/12dd269b0160491cc38bc87e8a388cf0.poster.avif?t=1731245171\" width=600 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2711300/extras/12dd269b0160491cc38bc87e8a388cf0.webm?t=1731245171\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2711300/extras/12dd269b0160491cc38bc87e8a388cf0.mp4?t=1731245171\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow the three young heroes Isaac, Clara and Naoto as they journey across the land to recover the Staff of Ultimate Power from the heinous <strong>Varakh</strong> and prevent <strong>the end of the world</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore</strong> and <strong>fight</strong> your way through the otherworldly and box-filled <strong>Basement Dimension</strong> and the luscious and overgrown <strong>Garden Forest</strong>!<strong> </strong>Meet and<strong> talk</strong> to whimsical characters and discover hidden stories!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2711300/extras/7aa73717f7a1b17962143a9a4678909f.poster.avif?t=1