t=1731245171\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2711300/extras/7bde79eac639198e8f7503553203df7f.mp4?t=1731245171\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect powerful <strong>stickers, equipment,</strong> and <strong>spells</strong> to upgrade the party and temporarily satiate your <i>unending hunger for content</i>!</p>",
